english_definitions: to do for (the sake of someone else)
to go to and from (a place)
to grow cold (from room temperature, e.g. in refrigerator)
to do over again (after -masu base of verb)
to give a present or gift
to treat (someone, e.g. to a meal)
amount necessary to fill a container (e.g. cupful, spoonful, etc.)
a long time (since the last time)
